		<li class="rounded p-2 hover:bg-gray-50">
			<a
				href="https://github.com/alyraffauf/slategreen"
				class="cactus-link inline-block font-bold text-green-600">slategreen</a
			> :: Developer-centric cloud-native OS based on <a
				href="https://fedoraproject.org/"
				class="cactus-link inline-block font-bold text-green-600 hover:text-green-800">Fedora</a
			> and <a href="https://github.com/alyraffauf/ugreen" class="text-green-600 hover:text-green-800"
				>ugreen</a
			>.
		</li> -->
